"Jockstrap 的泰勒·斯凯和乔治亚·埃勒里。信用。埃迪·惠兰 (1)" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Taylor-Skye-and-Georgia-Ellery-of-Jockstrap.-Credit.-Eddie-Whelan-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Taylor-Skye-and-Georgia-Ellery-of-Jockstrap.-Credit.-Eddie-Whelan-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Taylor-Skye-and-Georgia-Ellery-of-Jockstrap.-Credit.-Eddie-Whelan-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Taylor-Skye-and-Georgia-Ellery-of-Jockstrap.-Credit.-Eddie-Whelan-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Taylor-Skye-and-Georgia-Ellery-of-Jockstrap.-Credit.-Eddie-Whelan-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Taylor-Skye-and-Georgia-Ellery-of-Jockstrap.-Credit.-Eddie-Whelan-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jockstrap">Jockstrap</a>宣布推出“I&lt;3UQTINVU”，这是他们首张专辑的混音版本，由 Taylor Skye 制作。<b></b></p><ul><li aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/jockstrap-i-love-you-jennifer-b-review-radar-3305709">Jockstrap – “I Love You Jennifer B”评论：神奇、迷人的首次亮相 – 也是年度最佳之一</a></b></li></ul><p>《I&lt;3UQTINVU》是《I Love You Cutie, I Envy You》的缩写，是对 Jockstrap 2022 年专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/jockstrap-i-love-you-jennifer-b-review-radar-3305709" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《I Love You Jennifer B》</a>的更新。混音版由 Skye 策划，她与 Georgia Ellery 一起组成了 Jockstrap 二人组之一。</p><p> Skye 为《I Love You Jennifer B》中的每首歌制作了混音版，以在专辑创作过程中保持灵感。斯凯在一份新闻声明中说：“其中一些混音版已经有近三年的历史了，有些只有六个月的历史。” “在混音专辑时这样做让我保持理智。”</p><p>定于 11 月 3 日发行的《I&lt;3UQTINVU》已与 IAN STARR 合作的主打单曲《Red Eye》进行了预览。新单曲附有由 Liam Noonan 拍摄的音乐视频，其中 STARR、Ellery 和 Skye 在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/boygenius-fred-again-primal-scream-to-headline-scotlands-connect-festival-2023-3407807" target="_blank" rel="noopener">今年的 Connect Festival</a>上表演。 </p><p><iframe loading=